'''哈杰''' ({{lang-en|Hajjah}}，{{lang-ar|حجة}})是[[也门|也门]]西北部[[哈杰省|哈杰省]]的首府。位于首都[[萨那|萨那]]西北方127公里处，海拔1800米<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.yemen-nic.net/English%20site/SITE%20CONTAINTS/Tourism/Touristic%20sites/Hajjah/Hajjah.htm|title=Hajjah Governorate|publisher=Yemen National Information Centre|accessdate=October 21, 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100828113224/http://www.yemen-nic.net/English%20site/SITE%20CONTAINTS/Tourism/Touristic%20sites/Hajjah/Hajjah.htm|archivedate=2010年8月28日}}</ref>。2003年该地有人口53,887<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.statoids.com/yye.html|title=Districts of Yemen|publisher=Statoids|accessdate=October 21, 2010|archive-date=2010-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101129043227/http://statoids.com/yye.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

